## Conditional Statement
# if 
# syntax: 
# if condition : statement
# or
#  if condition:
#   statement-1
#   statement-2
#   statement-3
# if condition is true then statements will be executed.


# if-else
# syntax:
# if condition :
#   statement-1
#   statement-2
# else:
#   statement-3
#   statement-4
# if condition is true then first statements will be executed. other wise next statements will be executed.


# if-elif-else
# syntax:
# if condition :
#   statement-1
# elif condition:
#   statement-2
# elif condition:
#   statement-3
# else:
#   Default Action
# Based condition the corresponding action will be executed.
